<P>
   Business Day Front Page (All stories coded ``f'' unless
otherwise noted; transmission times are Eastern)
</P>
<P>
   (Lede story)
</P>
<P>
   INTERNET-SHOESALES (Undated) _ Developments concerning the use
of the Internet as a tool for selling shoes. By Saul Hansell.
</P>
<P>
   (Will move by 8:30 p.m.)
</P>
<P>
   (Main Display)
</P>
<P>
