</P>
<P>
   How Us magazine stacks up against its rivals.
</P>
<P>
   US_Weekly competition.pdf -- 2 x 4 -- (BC-US-MAG-MEDIA-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Us magazine,a monthly magazine, is scheduled to come out weekly
in March. Pdf file.
</P>
<P>
   PRIMEDIA_Publications -- 1 x 4 1/2--
(BC-PRIMEDIA-MULTIMEDIA-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Some of PrimediaUs publications, by division.
