<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-26 21:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6802 &Cx1f; tth-z
u e BC-FOOD-OWEN-COLUMN-SPI &LR;      09-26 0918
